# WAI-Harness — v4 tracking model (redressed S46)
#
# DURABLE work-state is TRACKED + restorable: lugs, savepoints, sessions, WAI-State,
# the hub registry, teachings_repo, learnings, initiatives, advisor definitions.
# Only DERIVED / regenerable runtime is ignored (a tool re-creates it; it is never
# the source of truth). This SUPERSEDES the prior blanket `spoke/local/** + hub/local/**`
# ignore, which made the home's work-state unrestorable.
#
# managed/ stays tracked + MANIFEST-MD5-verified (integrity checks are managed-scoped,
# so tracking local/ does not affect harness integrity/parity/upgrade verification).

# --- regenerable runtime (re-created by a tool; not source of truth) ---
**/runtime/
**/.autosave/
**/ozi-brief.json
**/octo-brief.json
**/wakeup-brief.json

# advisor-derived scans / reports / queues (regenerated every run):
**/WAI-Hub/advisors/*/reports/
**/WAI-Hub/advisors/*/scan_state.json
**/WAI-Hub/advisors/*/scan_history.jsonl
**/WAI-Hub/advisors/gardener/passes.jsonl
**/WAI-Hub/advisors/octo/council_directives.json
**/WAI-Hub/advisors/octo/hub_work_queue.json
**/WAI-Hub/advisors/octo/reports/
**/WAI-Hub/advisors/quartermaster/inventory.json
**/octo/job-queue.jsonl
**/octo/spoke-summaries/

# --- build / OS / secrets (never source) ---
**/__pycache__/
**/*.py[cod]
**/*$py.class
**/.pytest_cache/
**/.ruff_cache/
**/.DS_Store
.venv/
venv/
ENV/
env/
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local
**/.claude/settings.local.json
**/.claude/.provider
